caption.title: Simulated intervention results in decreasing the vector birth rate by the action of removing the places where mosquitoes lay the eggs.
caption.p:
A and B present the number of cases and the cumulative number of infect people, respectively. The solid blue line is the simulation without intervention ω
o = 0.0. The dashed red line presents the data for ω
o = 0.25, and the dotted yellow shows the data for ω
o = 0.5.
